第七届金投赏年会网易专场于10月21日在上海商城剧院举行，以品牌，是一种态度为主题，网易携手尼尔森发布年度十大态度关键词，网易门户市场部总经理
　　新意互动广告有限公司(CIG)成立于2002年， 总部设于北京，在上海、重庆、广州三地设有分公司， 员工300人。凭借聚集8年的网络全案代理丰富经验，CIG已成为中国最大的网络营销全案代理商之一。　　新意互动(CIG)是易车公司的全资子公司。2010年11月，易车公司于纽约证交所正式挂牌上市(股票代码：BITA)，是国内第一个上市的汽车互联网企业。　　CIG was established in 2002, With headquarter in Beijing, and 3 branches in Shanghai, Guangzhou, and Chongqing, over 300 employees in China. For 8 years digital marketing experience, CIG become the largest internet advertising agency for automakers in China.　　CIG is the subsidiary company of the Bitauto. November 17, 2010 Bitauto was officially listed on the New York stock exchange (stock code: BITA), is the first domestic auto internet company.　　他们的竞争优势/ ：Competitive advantage　　新意互动(CIG)定位为“数字时代的网络营销公司”，致力于专业的网络整合营销传播服务，包括网络广告投放、创意，网站建设与优化、网络公关、互动活动、无线营销及其他数字营销等服务。其长期坚持并贯彻“创意第一、策略第一、服务第一”的三大理念，赢得众多客户的信任，也荣获无数奖项与荣誉。CIG目前在行业内公司排行前十，互动创意排行第二名。　　CIG was dedicated to provide digital marketing solutions business, leverages our expertise in online marketing for the automotive industry by providing automakers with one-stop digital marketing solutions, including online public relations, online marketing campaigns and advertising agent services.　　CIG insist for a long time and implement the three concepts "creative,strategies, service", has won and entitled numerous awards and the trust of the majority of customers. CIG ranks the top ten in its field, the second place in the interactive creative field.　　CIG拥有技术一流的CG团队，2007年11月，福特蒙迪欧-致胜上市的产品网站，新意互动就应用了当时还比较新鲜的3D技术，开启汽车厂商对3D应用的先河，3D应用自此进入平民技术时代；在新媒体、新技术应用领域，CIG保持敏锐的嗅觉并力争为引领者，2009年初，新意互动引入AR(增强现实)技术，成功策划了国内汽车企业首次应用AR技术的新车发布会。　　CIG possesses the first-class technological CG team. On November 2007, CIG applied 3D technology creative the Ford-mondeo Launching website , which was relatively new at that time, ushering in the beginning that car manufacturers adopt 3D application. Since then, 3D applications has entered technology age for civilians. In the new media and new technology application domain, CIG strives to play the leading role with keen sense of smell. In early 2009, CIG successfully planned an Launching event by applying AR(augment reality) technology, in which AR technology was firstly applied by the domestic automobile enterprises.　　公司官网网址：www.ci-ad.com　　业务范围：新意互动(CIG)定位为“数字时代的网络营销公司”，致力于专业的网络整合营销传播服务，包括网络广告投放、创意，网站建设与优化、网络公关、互动活动、无线营销及其他数字营销等服务。
